Package gw.plugin.rateflow

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    CostDataBase
    Base class for CostData This does not need to contain anything, but is the base class for CostData so that it can be referenced by a Java plugin interface.
    ICostDataWrapper
    Required interface for a CostData wrapper.
    IImpactTestingPlugin
    Implementations of this plugin manage the creation and quoting of baseline periods and test periods as well as constraining the available rate books when quoting the test periods.
    IRateQueryLookupPlugin<T>
    A rate query lookup plugin provides the opportunity to implement custom failover logic in the even the primary lookup fails.
    IRateRoutineConfig  
    IRateRoutinePlugin
    This is the plugin interface used for RateRoutine configuration.
    QueryPreemptionResult
    Created by kbrower on 7/29/2015.
    RateBookPreloadPlugin
    Plugin for controlling rate book preload and export to rate routines JAR.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    RateBookEvent
    Various events in the rate book lifecycle that trigger an update of the rate routines JAR.
